  "title": "Ask for folder name if not provided in the arguments",
  "body": "## Bug description\r\n\r\nWhen the folder name is not provided, the CLI fails. This is an OK behavior when installed globally. However this is a problem with `yarn create` as yarn will check if there is a new version, which takes some time.\r\n\r\n## How to reproduce\r\n\r\n - `yarn create instantsearch-app`\r\n - yarn downloads stuff\r\n - fail because there is no folder provided\r\n - type again `yarn create instantsearch-app folder`\r\n - download again\r\n - now it's good\r\n\r\n## Expected behavior\r\n\r\nA better user experience would be to ask for the missing parameter.",
